meta.description: A blockade that began in early June has shut Qatar's only land crossing. But the small country's leader isn't bowing to pressure to change the non-conformist nation's ways. Charlie Rose reports.

title: Watch 60 Minutes: The Blockade of Qatar - Full show on CBS
